Entry.JapaneseText: ぜんたーい、止まれ！ 右向け〜、右っ！
<Red>ヴァルハラ<White>の方は 片付いたのか？
Entry.EnglishText: So you've been dismissed from the mission in Valhalla?

Entry.JapaneseText: いや。いよいよ 総力を投じることになって 援軍を頼みに戻ってきたんだ
Entry.EnglishText: I'm afraid not. We are strengthening our forces to provide backup.

Entry.JapaneseText: 絶対、ぶっ潰してこいよ。 グリッドの両親のかたきだ……！
Entry.EnglishText: Make them pay! What they've done to Grid's parents is unforgivable...

Entry.JapaneseText: グリッド……？ <CST>んちにいる 子どもか？
Entry.EnglishText: Grid...? You mean the kid that is over your house?

Entry.JapaneseText: ああ。あいつの両親…… 『シグルド』に殺されたんだよ……
Entry.EnglishText: Same kid. Those bastards killed his parents...

Entry.JapaneseText: あいつら、やること、 めちゃくちゃだ！
Entry.EnglishText: He's the proof this has gone way too far!

Entry.JapaneseText: 敵味方関係なく 無差別に殺しまくって……
Entry.EnglishText: Doesn't matter if they're enemies or allies to them. They kill anything they want!

Entry.JapaneseText: ああ……おまえの客だよ。 話を聞きたいんだってさ
Entry.EnglishText: They're visitors. They've been waiting to have a word with you.

Entry.JapaneseText: そうか。 でも、ごめんよ、 今は戦いの準備をしなきゃ
Entry.EnglishText: I see. I'm sorry but that'd have to wait. We're preparing for assault.

Entry.JapaneseText: そんなの、 したっぱに任せとけよ
Entry.EnglishText: Really, now? Just leave someone on charge.

Entry.JapaneseText: 大体、<MIN>とも ろくに会ってないんだろ？
Entry.EnglishText: Hell, have you met with <MIN> yet?

Entry.JapaneseText: 彼女も忙しい みたいだから……
Entry.EnglishText: That girl is very busy herself...

Entry.JapaneseText: すみません！ <CLE>さん、 ちょっといいですか！？
Entry.EnglishText: Excuse me! Mister <CLE>, could you spare me a second?
Yes! I'll be there right away!

Entry.JapaneseText: すまない、 ちょっと行ってくる
Entry.EnglishText: I apologize, I really have to go.
What crawled up his ass now?
This really does look like a dangerous situation.

Entry.JapaneseText: <CLE>さんと<MIN>さんって ……恋人なのかな？
Entry.EnglishText: Mister <CLE> and Miss <MIN> are...lovers aren't they?

Entry.JapaneseText: え？ あっと…… そういや、んなこと 本に書いてたかも……
Entry.EnglishText: Wh-what? W-well... It's not like...those types of things are written in books...

Entry.JapaneseText: だってオレ、 なんかそーゆーの よくわかんねーし……
Entry.EnglishText: Don't look at me! I don't know the first thing about it, either!

Entry.JapaneseText: ね、わたしたちで <CLE>さんたちを 会わせてあげらんないかな
Entry.EnglishText: Hey, why don't we make those two see each other?

Entry.JapaneseText: 会わせるったって どうすんだよ
Entry.EnglishText: And how exactly do you plan to do that?

Entry.JapaneseText: ふたりのお手伝いするとか。 忙しくて会えないんでしょ
Entry.EnglishText: We can replace them temporarily and relieve some of their workload.

Entry.JapaneseText: 『なりきり士』の力を使えば、 お手伝いできること なにかあるんじゃない？
Entry.EnglishText: I mean...After all, aren't Roleplayer powers originally meant to help people in need like this?

Entry.JapaneseText: ね、とにかく<MIN>さんに 会いに行ってみない？
Entry.EnglishText: Well, why don't we meet with <MIN> first? We can go from there.
